                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-509" type="surname" value="CARTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-509" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS CARTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. On the 15th of May I was on duty in Seven-dials, at about half-past four o'clock in the morning and saw the prisoner crossing the Dials with a bundle—I made towards him, he ran away—I followed, and came up with him in Leicester-street, Lei<lb></lb>cester-square—I secured, and found the bundle contained a clock.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360613-name-510" type="witnessName">
